collections.name: SPECTRUM by TheFormatix
collections.description:
SPECTRUM is a generative art collection created using JavaScript and the p5.js library, uploaded to the Ethereum blockchain. The collection consists of 250 unique artworks (NFTs ERC-721), each featuring a simple geometric abstraction filled with gradients of random colors. The background color is directly influenced by the main colors used in the artwork, creating harmonious combinations and dynamic transitions.
Each artwork is the result of an interaction between randomness and algorithm.
Special attention is given to 13 unique 1/1 rare artworks that incorporate special color spectra, adding variety to the collection.

Made by TheFormatix with love!

MARCH 2025
